DUnitX.MacOS.Console Namespace

Summary

Adding this unit to your project will register console support for the Mac OS.

Classes
 NameDescription
TDUnitXMacOSConsoleWriter

Internal Class and should not be created directly. Adding this unit to the uses will automatically register this class as a IDUnitXConsoleWriter in the DUnitX IOC Container.

Top
Remarks

It is recommended to add the DUnitX.AutoDetect.Console to your project uses instead of this unit directly.
